^bWhen we have 1@C/@D-P-1@S-P-1NT situation, NMF is more involved. In the following auctions:|
ht|I|cs|6|at|^B{|ia|,1DP1sp1nP2c|at|}^m OR|HT|I|at|^o{|ia|,1CP1SP1Np2d|at|} |
